::Shadow Wing::

She heard what Stegtron had said. She put her hands over her eyes and 
wanted to die right then and there.  She had wanted him to be more 
subtle about it. Her face turned a bright red.  She knew that 
Lunarpine would have her tail feathers nailed to the wall for this.
She couldn't even look at Lunarpine.  She just shuffled her feet 
along the ground. 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, TrikeJacob@n... wrote:
> Stegotron walks over to Lunarpine. 
> Stegotron: Your friend Shadow Wing told me to repair your damaged 
optics.
